s="edit_message">(1 edit)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>This was incredible. Even for a point-and-click game, this got me terrified thinking was in the next room. I won&#x27;t forget this, so will you be&nbsp;making any more points and click more?&nbsp;</p>  <div><button itchio aria-label="Click to activate YouTube embed" type="button" class="embed_preload youtube_preload" data-embed_code="&lt;iframe width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;281&quot; src=&quot;//www.youtube.com/embed/ld3UXLgBN74&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;" style="width: 250px; height: 140px; background: url(https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ld3UXLgBN74/hqdefault.jpg) 50% 50% no-repeat; background-size: cover"></button></div></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-7710684" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7710684,&quot;user_id&quot;:5092358}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/jedb"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzc0NDAxOTguanBn/25x25%23/MnYtuW.jpg)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/jedb">Julien Bartholini</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-04-29 10:27:48"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7710684">62 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Hello Stormzo :-D  I watched your let&#x27;s play last night. Bravo and  thank you for making a video on my game. It&#x27;s the kind of thing that  always makes me happy ^^.<br>I want to keep making games but I don&#x27;t know when and I don&#x27;t know what gameplay I would choose :^)<br>Thanks again and greetings from France !  </p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-7657040" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7657040,&quot;user_id&quot;:7842946}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/kittycatjessi"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-cyan.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/kittycatjessi">kittycatjessi</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-04-19 03:32:34"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7657040">72 days ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(1 edit)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>This was really good! I used to play a lot of these types of games when I was younger. Now I know that they still scare the crap out of me. It&#x27;s one of those that leaves a lasting impression. Nice bathroom scene by the way ;)</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-7657759" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7657759,&quot;user_id&quot;:5092358}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/jedb"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzc0NDAxOTguanBn/25x25%23/MnYtuW.jpg)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/jedb">Julien Bartholini</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-04-19 08:44:27"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7657759">72 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p></p><p>Thanks you very much kittycatjessi ! :-)<br>Around 2010 I was playing short games of this type, themselves inspired by the point n click of the 90s. That&#x27;s what made me want to make this little game. I&#x27;m glad you like it.<br>Thanks again and greetings from France !<br><br>Take. It&#x27;s free.<br><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzExOTA5NjMzLmpwZw==/original/cc8NWa.jpg" loading="lazy"><br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-7632863" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7632863,&quot;user_id&quot;:6505077}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/watormalon"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-red.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/watormalon">Watormalon</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-04-14 21:00:31"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7632863">76 days ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(1 edit)</span> <span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>i came back to play this game after a while (still an amazing game)&nbsp;&nbsp;then red the comments and just love how you just respond to everyones posts and i think that really admirable</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-7637635" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7637635,&quot;user_id&quot;:5092358}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden vie