onem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/jedb"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzc0NDAxOTguanBn/25x25%23/MnYtuW.jpg)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/jedb">Julien Bartholini</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-03-02 00:51:32"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7420960">120 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+2)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p></p><p>I don&#x27;t understand. In nearly a year and a half out of nearly 100,000 players, never once has anyone come to tell me about such a bug. Sorry for not being able to help you more. I would almost need a video of your part to be able to understand. I can&#x27;t guarantee you anything but you should try to play on another browser (if you haven&#x27;t already).</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-7402197" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7402197,&quot;user_id&quot;:3188393}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/snootysnootgames"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzQyMzIwNzUucG5n/25x25%23/Doi8wC.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/snootysnootgames">Sfunk92</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-02-27 02:08:38"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7402197">123 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>This was a really fun 20 minutes. The atmosphere was setup pretty well. The monsters looked pretty goofy though lol The jump scares were pretty well telegraphed too so if you payed attention while playing, there wasn&#x27;t much concern with getting caught off gaurd by a jump scare.&nbsp;</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div id="post-7402389" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7402389,&quot;user_id&quot;:5092358}" class="community_post has_replies is_reply has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/jedb"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzc0NDAxOTguanBn/25x25%23/MnYtuW.jpg)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/jedb">Julien Bartholini</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-02-27 03:03:28"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7402389">123 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p></p><p>Thanks Sfunk92 :-)<br>I&#x27;m someone who doesn&#x27;t like jumpscare. Especially when they are poorly integrated into a story. My thing is rather the deceptively comfortable atmosphere. When a warm place becomes more and more disturbing.</p>  <p>Thank you so much for playing my game and greetings from France !</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-7415103" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:7415103,&quot;user_id&quot;:3188393}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fjedb.itch.io%2Finvitationem&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" height="20" width="20" version="1.1" aria-hidden viewbox="0